-- Datang Parent's Renewable-Energy Public Offer Won't Affect Datang Power
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-04-20T04:30:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-20/datang-parent-s-renewable-energy-public-offer-won-t-affect-datang-power.html

          
          
             China Datang Corp.’s plan to list
its renewable energy unit in an initial public offering won’t
affect Datang International Power Generation Co., Cao Jingshan,
the vice chairman of Datang International, told reporters in
Hong Kong today.    
